T1  - Making a Difference in the Teamwork: Linking Team Prosocial Motivation to Team Processes and Effectiveness
AU  - Hu, Jia
AU  - Liden, Robert C.
Y1  - 2014/06/20
PY  - 2014
DA  - 2015/08/01
N1  - doi: 10.5465/amj.2012.1142
DO  - 10.5465/amj.2012.1142
T2  - Academy of Management Journal
JF  - Academy of Management Journal
JO  - AMJ
SP  - 1102
